Ding is a graphical dictionary lookup program for X11. It is based on the 
TK GUI toolkit and the agrep tool for searching. Ding offers a lot of 
configuration options such as search preferences, interface language, 
colors, etc. It includes history and help functions as well as useful key 
and mouse bindings for quick and easy lookups.

This package comes with an English-German dictionary (> 345,000 entries).
